    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Indication of multiple materials being used for a group, set, or other configuration of multiple works, including visual works, audio works, written works, or other types of works. For the indication of multiple materials being used on one single work, use "mixed media."</Note_Text>
